      comments: []
    - name: '5: '
      title: 
      number: 5
      content: No one can be compared to God, enthroned on high!
      comments: []
    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: He stoops down to look upon the sky and the earth.
      comments: []
    - name: '7: '
      title: 
      number: 7
      content: He promotes the poor, picking them up from the dirt,and rescues the
