        content: "  Or  , which means \u201Cpraise.\u201D    "
    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: The Red Sea waters saw them coming and ran the other way!Then later,
        the Jordan River toomoved aside so that they could all pass through.
      comments: []
    - name: '4: '
      title: 
      number: 4
      content: The land shuddered with fear.Mountains and hills shook with dread.
