          See  .  "
    - name: '17-18: '
      title: 
      number: 17-18
      content: "Every single moment you are thinking of me!How precious and wonderful
        to considerthat you cherish me constantly in your every thought!O&nbsp;God,
        your desires toward me are morethan the grains of sand on every shore!When
        I awake each morning, you\u2019re still with me."
      comments: []
    - name: '17-18: '
      title: 
