      comments: []
    - name: '19: '
      title: 
      number: 19
      content: "O&nbsp;God, come and slay these bloodthirsty, murderous men!For I
        cry out, \u201CDepart from me, you wicked ones!\u201D"
      comments: []
    - name: '20: '
      title: 
      number: 20
      content: See how they blaspheme your sacred nameand lift up themselves against
