      comments: []
    - name: '23: '
      title: 
      number: 23
      content: God, I invite your searching gaze into my heart.Examine me through
        and through;find out everything that may be hidden within me.Put me to the
        test and sift through all my anxious cares.
      comments: []
    - name: '24: '
      title: 
      number: 24
      content: "See if there is any path of pain I\u2019m walking on,and lead me
        back to your glorious, everlasting way\u2014the path that brings me back
        to you."
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - name: '1: A Prayer for Protection'
      title: A Prayer for Protection
      number: 1
      content: "For the Pure and Shining OneKing David\u2019s poetic songLord, protect
        me from this evil one!Rescue me from these violent schemes!"
