    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: "When the leaders and judges are condemned,falling upon the rocks
        of justice, [[COMMENT(0)]]then they\u2019ll know my words to them were true!"
      comments:
      - number: 141:6
        content: '  See  .  '
    - name: '7: '
      title: 
      number: 7
      content: Like an earthquake splits open the earth,so the world of hell will
