        content: "  Or \u201Ctakes pleasure in,\u201D \u201Cdelights in,\u201D \u201Csets
          his affection on,\u201D \u201Cenjoys,\u201D \u201Cfinds pleasing,\u201D
          \u201Cis satisfied with.\u201D      Or \u201Cwho wait for his loyal, unfailing
          love.\u201D    "
    - name: '12: '
      title: 
      number: 12
      content: Jerusalem, praise the Lord! Zion, worship your God!
      comments: []
    - name: '13: '
      title: 
      number: 13
      content: For he has strengthened the authority of your gates.He even blesses
        you with more children.
      comments: []
    - name: '14: '
      title: 
      number: 14
      content: "He\u2019s the one who brings peace to your borders, [[COMMENT(0)]]feeding
        you the most excellent of fare."
      comments:
      - number: 147:14
        content: "  The Septuagint reads \u201CHe makes peace your borders.\u201D  "
    - name: '15: '
      title: 
      number: 15
      content: He sends out his orders throughout the world;his words run as swift
        messengers, bringing them to pass.
      comments: []
    - name: '16: '
      title: 
      number: 16
      content: He blankets the earth with glistening snow,painting the landscape
        with frost.
      comments: []
    - name: '17: '
      title: 
      number: 17
      content: "Sleet and hail fall from the sky,causing waters to freeze before
        winter\u2019s icy blast."
      comments: []
    - name: '18: '
      title: 
      number: 18
      content: Then he speaks his word and it all melts away;as the warm spring winds
        blow, the streams begin to flow.
      comments: []
    - name: '19: '
      title: 
      number: 19
      content: In the same way, he speaks his word to Jacob,and to Israel he brings
        his life-giving instruction.
      comments: []
    - name: '20: '
      title: 
      number: 20
      content: He has dealt with Israel differently than with any other people,for
        they have received his laws.Hallelujah! Praise the Lord!
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - name: '1: The Cosmic Chorus of Praise'
      title: The Cosmic Chorus of Praise
      number: 1
      content: Hallelujah! Praise the Lord! Let the skies be filled with praiseand
        the highest heavens with the shouts of glory!
      comments: []
    - name: '2: '
      title: 
      number: 2
      content: "Go ahead\u2014praise him, all you his messengers!Praise him some
        more, all you heavenly hosts!"
      comments: []
    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: "Keep it up, sun and moon!Don\u2019t stop now, all you twinkling stars
        of light!"
      comments: []
    - name: '4: '
      title: 
      number: 4
      content: "Take it up even higher\u2014up to the highest heavens,until the cosmic
        chorus thunders his praise! [[COMMENT(0)]]"
      comments:
      - number: 148:4
        content: "  Poetic implication in the text. The literal Hebrew reads \u201C[Praise
          him] you waters above the sky.\u201D  "
    - name: '5: '
      title: 
      number: 5
      content: "Let the entire universe erupt with praise to God.He spoke and created
        it all\u2014from nothing to something."
      comments: []
    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: He established the cosmos to last forever,and he stands behind his
        commandsso his orders will never be revoked.
      comments: []
    - name: '7: '
      title: 
      number: 7
      content: "Let the earth join in with this parade of praise!You mighty creatures
        of the ocean\u2019s depths,echo in exaltation!"
      comments: []
    - name: '8: '
      title: 
      number: 8
      content: "Lightning, hail, snow, clouds,and the stormy winds that fulfill his
        word\u2014"
      comments: []
    - name: '9: '
      title: 
      number: 9
      content: bring your melody, O&nbsp;mountains and hills;trees of the forest
        and field, harmonize your praise!
      comments: []
    - name: '10-12: '
      title: 
      number: 10-12
      content: Praise him, all beasts and birds, mice and men,kings, queens, princes,
        and princesses,young men and maidens, children and babes,old and young alike,
        everyone everywhere!
      comments: []
    - name: '10-12: '
      title: 
      number: 10-12
      content: Praise him, all beasts and birds, mice and men,kings, queens, princes,
        and princesses,young men and maidens, children and babes,old and young alike,
        everyone everywhere!
      comments: []
    - name: '10-12: '
      title: 
      number: 10-12
      content: Praise him, all beasts and birds, mice and men,kings, queens, princes,
        and princesses,young men and maidens, children and babes,old and young alike,
        everyone everywhere!
      comments: []
    - name: '13: '
      title: 
      number: 13
      content: Let them all join in with this orchestra of praise.For the name of
        the Lord is the only name we raise!His stunning splendor ascends higher than
        the heavens.
      comments: []
    - name: '14: '
      title: 
      number: 14
      content: He anoints his people with strength and authority,showing his great
        favor to all his godly lovers,even to his princely people, Israel,who are
        so close to his heart.Hallelujah! Praise the Lord!
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - name: '1: Triumphant Praise'
      title: Triumphant Praise
      number: 1
      content: "Hallelujah! Praise the Lord!It\u2019s time to sing to God a brand-new
        song [[COMMENT(0)]]so that all his holy people will hear how wonderful he
        is!"
      comments:
      - number: 149:1
        content: "  Or \u201Ca spontaneous song.\u201D  "
    - name: '2: '
      title: 
      number: 2
      content: May Israel be enthused with joy because of him,and may the sons of
        Zion pour outtheir joyful praises to their King.
      comments: []
    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: "Break forth with dancing!Make music and sing God\u2019s praises with
        the rhythm of drums!"
      comments: []
    - name: '4: '
      title: 
      number: 4
      content: For he enjoys his faithful lovers.He adorns the humble with his beauty,and
        he loves to give them victory.
      comments: []
    - name: '5: '
      title: 
      number: 5
      content: His godly lovers triumph in the glory of God,and their joyful praises
        will rise even while others sleep.
      comments: []
    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: "God\u2019s high and holy praises fill their mouths,for their shouted
        praises are their weapons of war!"
      comments: []
    - name: '7: '
      title: 
      number: 7
      content: "These warring weapons will bring vengeanceon the nations and every
        resistant power\u2014"
      comments: []
    - name: '8: '
      title: 
      number: 8
      content: to bind kings with chains and rulers with iron shackles.
      comments: []
    - name: '9: '
      title: 
      number: 9
      content: Praise-filled warriors will enforcethe judgment decreed against their
        enemies.This is the honor he gives to all his godly lovers.Hallelujah! Praise
        the Lord!
      comments: []
